<body>

<h2>반응형 결제 양식</h2>
<p>브라우저 창 크기를 조절하여 효과를 확인하세요. 화면 너비가 800px 미만이면 두 열을 옆이 아니라 위로 쌓도록 만듭니다.</p>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-75">
    <div class="container">
      <form action="/action_page.php">
      
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-50">
            <h3>청구 주소</h3>
            <label for="fname"><i class="fa fa-user"></i> 전체 이름</label>
            <input type="text" id="fname" name="firstname" placeholder="홍길동">
            <label for="email"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> 이메일</label>
            <input type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="hong@example.com">
            <label for="adr"><i class="fa fa-address-card-o"></i> 주소</label>
            <input type="text" id="adr" name="address" placeholder="서울시 강남구">
            <label for="city"><i class="fa fa-institution"></i> 도시</label>
            <input type="text" id="city" name="city" placeholder="서울">

            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-50">
                <label for="state">지역</label>
                <input type="text" id="state" name="state" placeholder="서울">
              </div>
              <div class="col-50">
                <label for="zip">우편번호</label>
                <input type="text" id="zip" name="zip" placeholder="100-000">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-50">
            <h3>결제</h3>
            <label for="fname">카드 종류</label>
            <div class="icon-container">
              <i class="fa fa-cc-visa" style="color:navy;"></i>
              <i class="fa fa-cc-amex" style="color:blue;"></i>
              <i class="fa fa-cc-mastercard" style="color:red;"></i>
              <i class="fa fa-cc-discover" style="color:orange;"></i>
            </div>
            <label for="cname">카드 소유자 이름</label>
            <input type="text" id="cname" name="cardname" placeholder="홍길동">
            <label for="ccnum">신용카드 번호</label>
            <input type="text" id="ccnum" name="cardnumber" placeholder="1111-2222-3333-4444">
            <label for="expmonth">유효 기간</label>
            <input type="text" id="expmonth" name="expmonth" placeholder="12월">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-50">
                <label for="expyear">만료 연도</label>
                <input type="text" id="expyear" name="expyear" placeholder="2024">
              </div>
              <div class="col-50">
                <label for="cvv">CVV</label>
                <input type="text" id="cvv" name="cvv" placeholder="352">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" checked="checked" name="sameadr"> 배송 주소와 동일
        </label>
        <input type="submit" value="계속해서 체크아웃" class="btn">
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-25">
    <div class="container">
      <h4>장바구니 <span class="price" style="color:black"><i class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></i> <b>4</b></span></h4>
      <p><a href="#">제품 1</a> <span class="price">$15</span></p>
      <p><a href="#">제품 2</a> <span class="price">$5</span></p>
      <p><a href="#">제품 3</a> <span class="price">$8</span></p>
      <p><a href="#">제품 4</a> <span class="price">$2</span></p>
      <hr>
      <p>총액 <span class="price" style="color:black"><b>$30</b></span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

